## Step 5: Calculate New APP Mass

**Refactored Code**:
```typescript
const calculateBasePremium = (items: Item[]): number => {
  // Check for 3 identical components building block
  if (
    items.length === 3 &&
    items.every((item) => item.type === "component")
  ) {
    return 60; // Building block premium
  }

  const itemType = items[0]?.type;
  return BASE_PREMIUMS[itemType ?? ""] ?? 0;
};

export const calculateQuote = (input: QuoteInput): number => {
  const basePremium = calculateBasePremium(input.items);
  return basePremium + PROCESSING_FEE;
};
```

Component Count:
- Constants: 3 (3, "component", 60) - ×1 = 3
- Bindings: 5 (items, input.items, PROCESSING_FEE, itemType, basePremium, input) - ×1 = 6
- Invocations: 4 (items.length, items.every, calculateBasePremium, item.type) - ×2 = 8
- Conditionals: 3 (if && condition, itemType ?? "", ?? 0) - ×4 = 12
- Loops: 1 (every method) - ×5 = 5
- Assignments: 2 (itemType =, basePremium =) - ×6 = 12

